    <etym xml:lang="ru">Начальная дигорская группа %iærw%i- восходит обычно к %ivr%i-: <ref
            type="xr" target="#entry_ærwæz"/> из *%ivraza%i-, %iærwæd%i (и. <ref type="xr"
            target="#entry_iræd"/>) из *%ivrata%i; %iærwagæs%i могло получиться из %ivṛ%i- +
        %iākas-%i „казаться (%iākas%i-) верным (%ivṛ%i-)“, „принять за верное“. Ср. <ref type="xr"
            target="#entry_kæsyn"/> в значении ‘казаться’, а для первой части — <ref type="xr"
            target="#entry_wyrnyn"/> ‘верить’, <mentioned xml:lang="ru"
            ><lang/><w>вера</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="goh"
        ><lang/><w>wār</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"
        ><lang/><w>verus</w></mentioned>.</etym>
    <etym xml:lang="en">The initial digor group %iærw%i- usually traces back to %ivr%i-:<ref
            type="xr" target="#entry_ærwæz"/> from *%ivraza%i-, %iærwæd%i (Iron <ref type="xr"
            target="#entry_iræd"/>) from *%ivrata%i; %iærwagæs%i could have been derived from
        %ivṛ%i- + %iākas-%i "to seem (%iākas%i-) true (%ivṛ%i-)", "to take something for a right
        thing". Compare <ref type="xr" target="#entry_kæsyn"/> in the meaning ‘to seem’, and as for
        the first part — <ref type="xr" target="#entry_wyrnyn"/> ‘believe’, <mentioned xml:lang="ru"
                ><lang/><w>vera</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="goh"
            ><lang/><w>wār</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"
        ><lang/><w>verus</w></mentioned>.</etym>
